land.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Prince&amp;rft.pub=J.M.+Dent%2C+London%2C+England&amp;rft.date=1908&amp;rft.aulast=Machiavelli&amp;rft.aufirst=Niccol%C3%B2&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Febooks.adelaide.edu.au%2Fm%2Fmachiavelli%2Fniccolo%2Fm149p%2Fchapter14.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADecision+game\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite id=\"CITEREFvon_Moltke1894\" class=\"citation\">von Moltke, Hellmuth (1894), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://archive.org/details/moltkestactical00armegoog\"><i>Moltke's Tactical Problems</i></a>, (Karl von Donat, translator), W.H. Allen, London, England.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Moltke%27s+Tactical+Problems&amp;rft.pub=W.H.+Allen%2C+London%2C+England&amp;rft.date=1894&amp;rft.aulast=von+Moltke&amp;rft.aufirst=Hellmuth&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.org%2Fdetails%2Fmoltkestactical00armegoog&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADecision+game\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li>\n<li><cite id=\"CITEREFSchmitt1994\" class=\"citation\">Schmitt, John F. (1994), <i>Mastering Tactics:  A Tactical Decision Games Workbook</i>, Marine Corps Association, Quantico, Virginia.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Mastering+Tactics%3A++A+Tactical+Decision+Games+Workbook&amp;rft.pub=Marine+Corps+Association%2C+Quantico%2C+Virginia&amp;rft.date=1994&amp;rft.aulast=Schmitt&amp;rft.aufirst=John+F.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADecision+game\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2274\nCached time: 20180919130658\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic